data.description: This immaculately maintained and beautifully updated 3 bedroom/2 bathroom pool home is perfect for entertaining your family and friends. The spacious living room offers plenty of natural light and room to relax to watch your favorite show. Whip up the perfect meal in the modern kitchen boasts granite counter tops, wood cabinets, stainless steel LG appliances and overlooks the pool. The master bedroom is a relaxing retreat with an en suite bathroom (Granite counter tops, wood cabinet & shower stall), plush carpet and a sliding glass door to the pool. Down the hall are 2 additional generous-sized bedroom, an updated hall bathroom and a walk-in hall closet. The bonus room is currently set up as a fun game room, but it could easily be an office, den and family room. Bask in the FL sunshine by taking a dip in your sparkling inground pool or lounge with a good book under the covered patio. The fenced back yard offers plenty of privacy, lush green grass and a shed for extra storage. The over-sized 2 car garage includes washer and dryer hook-up, a walk-in storage closet, additional storage space, and a wide driveway for added parking. Other spectacular updates and features include; new flat roof over back patio (2022), new gutters (2022), new concrete driveway (2022), main water & sewer lines original pipes re-lined (2022), main water shut-off valve replaced by city (2023), new duct work (2020), insulation added to attic (2020), Thermal/Insulated double pane wind impact glass storm windows and sliders installed throughout (2020), new pool pump/pool resurfaced (2020), vinyl fence, laminate flooring in main living areas, carpet in bedrooms, tile floors in both bathrooms, and situated on a corner lot. Conveniently located to the beaches, shopping, restaurants and interstate access. There's nothing left to do, but move in!
